OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1772651486
OL,3,CInquest told grandmother only
OL,4,Cdiagnosed with rabies after
OL,5,Cpsychiatrist visit
OL,7,FA grandmother who died from rabies
OL,8,Ffour months after she was scratched by
OL,9,Fa stray dog in Morocco was only
OL,10,Fdiagnosed after a psychiatrist was
OL,11,Fcalled in to assess her deteriorating
OL,12,Fsymptoms, an inquest jury in Sheffield
OL,13,Fhas been told.
OL,15,FFifty-nine-year-old Yvonne Ford was
OL,16,Fscratched on a Moroccan beach during a
OL,17,Ffamily holiday in February last year.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1772651486
OL,3,CInquest told grandmother only
OL,4,Cdiagnosed with rabies after
OL,5,Cpsychiatrist visit
OL,7,FSpeaking to ITV's This Morning, her
OL,8,Fhusband Ron, said in July last year:
OL,9,F"Two days before we came home, we're
OL,10,Fon the beach outside the hotel, and
OL,11,Fthere were lots of dogs running about
OL,12,Feverywhere, and there was a puppy
OL,13,Factually underneath the sunbed of
OL,14,FYvonne's.
OL,16,F"She put her leg down, it startled the
OL,17,Fdog, and it just scratched her. It
OL,18,Fdidn't bleed, it didn't really mark
OL,19,Fher."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
