PN,36603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1772651486
OL,3,CInquest told grandmother only
OL,4,Cdiagnosed with rabies after
OL,5,Cpsychiatrist visit
OL,7,FToday an inquest heard how rabies was
OL,8,Fonly diagnosed after Mrs Ford was
OL,9,Freferred to the mental health team at
OL,10,FBarnsley Hospital in June 2025 and a
OL,11,Fpsychiatrist asked her family about
OL,12,Fher travel history.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1772651486
OL,3,CInquest told grandmother only
OL,4,Cdiagnosed with rabies after
OL,5,Cpsychiatrist visit
OL,7,FPsychiatrist Alexander Burns told the
OL,8,Finquest how he was called to assess
OL,9,FMrs Ford, who was on the hospital's
OL,10,Fshort stay ward, because colleagues on
OL,11,Fthat unit had been struggling to
OL,12,Fdiagnose what was wrong with her and
OL,13,Fwere concerned her symptoms -
OL,14,Fincluding hallucinations,
OL,15,Fdisorientation and high levels of
OL,16,Fanxiety.
OL,18,FA junior doctor from Barnsley hospital
OL,19,Ftold the jury that because there was
OL,20,Fno diagnosis, all the hospital could
OL,21,Fdo was to treat her symptoms.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1772651486
OL,3,CInquest told grandmother only
OL,4,Cdiagnosed with rabies after
OL,5,Cpsychiatrist visit
OL,7,FDr Burns said he first asked about
OL,8,Fforeign travel because he suspected
OL,9,FLyme disease, which is caused by tick
OL,10,Fbites.
OL,12,FHe said: "I was informed by her
OL,13,Fhusband that, on February 10 2025,
OL,14,FYvonne was bitten by a stray dog on a
OL,15,Fbeach in Morocco whilst on holiday.
OL,16,FThe bite had pierced her skin. The
OL,17,Fshort stay unit medical team were not
OL,18,Fpreviously aware of that information."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1772651486
OL,3,CInquest told grandmother only
OL,4,Cdiagnosed with rabies after
OL,5,Cpsychiatrist visit
OL,7,FToday's inquest heard she did not seek
OL,8,Ftreatment as the wound was minor and
OL,9,Fcleaned with a wet wipe.
OL,11,FDr Burns told the inquest he became
OL,12,F"concerned that the diagnosis may be
OL,13,Frabies, in the context of the stray
OL,14,Fdog bite in Morocco and the various
OL,15,Fneurological symptoms".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1772651486
OL,3,CInquest told grandmother only
OL,4,Cdiagnosed with rabies after
OL,5,Cpsychiatrist visit
OL,7,FThe inquest heard how Mrs Ford was
OL,8,Fassessed by Dr Burns four days
OL,9,Ffollowing her initial arrival at
OL,10,FBarnsley hospital on June 2 2025. She
OL,11,Fwas transferred to an infectious
OL,12,Fdisease unit at Sheffield Royal
OL,13,FHallamshire Hospital where she died on
OL,14,FJune 11.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1772651486
OL,3,CInquest told grandmother only
OL,4,Cdiagnosed with rabies after
OL,5,Cpsychiatrist visit
OL,7,FThere have only been 26 cases of
OL,8,Frabies in the UK since 1946.
OL,9,FInfectious diseases expert Katharine
OL,10,FCartwright, from Sheffield Teaching
OL,11,FHospitals, told the jury how rabies is
OL,12,Fa virus that is 100% fatal once the
OL,13,Fsymptoms begin to show.
OL,15,FShe added that post-exposure
OL,16,Fadministration of a vaccine can help
OL,17,Fin some circumstances before the
OL,18,Fsymptoms begin.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1772651486
OL,3,CInquest told grandmother only
OL,4,Cdiagnosed with rabies after
OL,5,Cpsychiatrist visit
OL,7,FDr Cartwright was asked by Mrs Ford's
OL,8,Ffamily about the treatment she
OL,9,Freceived at Barnsley Hospital in the
OL,10,Ftime she was in the unit.
OL,12,FShe said it appeared that Mrs Ford
OL,13,Fbegan to exhibit symptoms at the end
OL,14,Fof May and, therefore, there was
OL,15,Fnothing that could have been done at
OL,16,FBarnsley Hospital that would have
OL,17,Fsaved her.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1772651486
OL,3,CInquest told grandmother only
OL,4,Cdiagnosed with rabies after
OL,5,Cpsychiatrist visit
OL,7,FShe said the illness was "incredibly
OL,8,Frare" and the collection of symptoms
OL,9,Fwere "challenging" for the medics in
OL,10,FBarnsley.
OL,12,FDr Cartwright told the inquest: "I
OL,13,Fthink the doctors did their best."
OL,15,FThe doctor said that, in 100 cases of
OL,16,Frabies in America since 2000, half
OL,17,Fwere only diagnosed after the patient
OL,18,Fhad died.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G10/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
